# Libraries

requests
beautifulsoup4

1. requests – HTTP requests
2. BeautifulSoup or lxml – HTML/XML parsing
3. urllib – URL parsing & normalization
4. Selenium – For crawling dynamic JavaScript websites (optional, heavier)
5. Scrapy – (If using a full crawling framework)

6. scikit-learn – TF-IDF, keyword vectorization

7. Dash / Streamlit / Flask – to show crawled data, keyword frequency
8. matplotlib / seaborn – for simple bar charts, word clouds
